            <section xml:id="d3/d10/class_modular_1_1_application_1ab096c671befd594e22708a02babcbeef">
                <title>static get_current_page ()</title> <emphasis></emphasis>
                
<para>Try to get page from Director and if in CMS then get it from CMS page, fallback to <link linkend="d6/d68/class_modular_1_1_controller">Controller</link> url via page_for_path.</para>

<para><formalpara><title>Returns: </title>

<para>|| </para>
</formalpara>
</para>

            </section>
            <section xml:id="d3/d10/class_modular_1_1_application_1a548c021d3c4fe5a3f376c22956b2f65a">
                <title>static requirements_path ()</title> <emphasis></emphasis>
                
<para>Override to provide current theme folder if requirements_path not set.</para>

<para><formalpara><title>Returns: </title>

<para>string </para>
</formalpara>
</para>

            </section>
            <section xml:id="d3/d10/class_modular_1_1_application_1a042d10ca7d0782adc2a871c07c288007">
                <title>static device_mode ()</title> <emphasis></emphasis>
                
<para>Return the device mode, e.g. &apos;mobile&apos;, &apos;desktop&apos;, &apos;default&apos;. At the moment just uses domain_theme. TODO: allow this to be found out in alternative ways, e.g. UserAgent </para>

            </section>
            <section xml:id="d3/d10/class_modular_1_1_application_1a605b07766c1bed3ff909fa8362f9985f">
                <title>static domain_theme ()</title> <emphasis></emphasis>
                
<para>Return the theme name matching on domain name via config.theme_domains</para>

<para><formalpara><title>Returns: </title>

<para>string </para>
</formalpara>
</para>

            </section>
            <section xml:id="d3/d10/class_modular_1_1_application_1a837267adf501aa1b29ad40505bc10755">
                <title>static hostname ()</title> <emphasis></emphasis>
                
<para>Return the server host name from file to url mappings. For cli mode you&apos;ll need to make sure a FILE_TO_URL_MAPPING is setup in environment file for the server.</para>

<para><formalpara><title>Returns: </title>

<para>string </para>
</formalpara>
